(27, 9, 12, 22, 'ColorStay™ Blot Setting Powder', 'colorstay™-blot-setting-powder', 'MK-Face123', '200', 'new product,top product', 'Small,Midium,Large', 'Red,Blue,Black', '120$', '99$', 'A setting powder with blotting power! Revlon ColorStay™ Blot Setting Powder is a mattifying powder fused with a shielding blend that provides non-stop matte for up to 16 hours. Triple-power action mattifies, absorbs oil and reduces the appearance of pores while controlling shine all day.', '<p><span style=\"font-family: AustinRoman, \'Times New Roman\', Roman, Georgia, serif; font-size: 25.6px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">A setting powder with blotting power!&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 25.6px; font-family: AustinRoman, \'Times New Roman\', Roman, Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background: white;\">Revlon ColorStay&trade; Blot Setting Powder is a mattifying powder fused with a shielding blend that provides non-stop matte for up to 16 hours. Triple-power action mattifies,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 25.6px; font-family: AustinRoman, \'Times New Roman\', Roman, Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">absorbs oil and reduces&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 25.6px; font-family: AustinRoman, \'Times New Roman\', Roman, Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background: white;\">the appearance of pores while controlling shine all day. The silky-soft formula creates a flawless matte finish that won&rsquo;t leave a chalky film on your skin, plus no photo flashback.&nbsp;</span><span style=\